                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1169" type="given" value="EDMUND"></interp>EDMUND GREENING</persName>
                  </hi>. I was passing through Mansfield-street, and heard a person call, "Stop him"—the coachman pointed to the prisoner, who was running with the coat under his arm—he threw it down, and I caught him.</p>
